
Bello Todo respects your privacy.

## Information Collection and Use
The extension may collect and store the following information solely to provide its core functionality:
Tasks and preferences saved by the user
Google account information (email and basic profile) when Google Sign-In is used
Google Sign-In is required to use the core features of the extension.

## Data Storage
All task data is stored locally in the user’s browser using Chrome storage.
If Google Sign-In is enabled, data may be associated with the user’s account for personalization and syncing purposes.

## Data Sharing
- Bello Todo does not sell, rent, or share user data with third parties.
- No data is used for advertising or tracking purposes.

## Website Access
The extension may inject a user-initiated overlay into the currently active webpage to enable focus and task management features.
The extension does not read or collect website content.

## Security
Reasonable measures are taken to protect user data. No sensitive personal information is intentionally collected.
Changes
This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page.

